channel.title: How do I find my server I.P.?
channel.description:
K. This is my first topic I've posted on these forums. I downloaded Testscape and got on it with the port 43594. I was wondering how to find my server I.P.... I never made a server before and I don't know what people are talking about when they say open up client.java and more stuff... I made a Ham Network and thats it... So will someone PLEASE tell me how to find my server I.P. and how to open up the Java things to enter my codes?
Thank you very much!
Rich is very nice!
